Sandstorm Gold Ltd.


            
            Sandstorm Gold Ltd. is a resource based company, which focuses on acquiring gold and other precious metal purchase agreements and royalties from companies that have advanced stage development projects or operating mines. It provides upfront financing to gold mining companies that are looking for capital and in return, receives a gold streaming agreement. The company was founded by Nolan Watson and David I. Awram on March 23, 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




